OK folks This is to let you know what happened and why there seems to be a great deal of problems and strife from one point of view.<br>
There was an awesome idea put forth by Wyrd , Qiara and some others of the 50+ people. Their idea was , in a nutshell , to maximize their playtime and to get practice at raiding by having a monthly/weekly (hadn't been fixed yet) get together that had hard rules about attendance and a rotating system to decide where they were going.<br>
This in and of itself was a wonderful idea and the ability that it would have given for people to experience new places and gather raid experience and pass that on to the rest of the Guild was very admirable.<br>
There was just one problem that caused all this strife in my mind.The planning of this new group , dubbed &quot;The Book Club&quot; , was done on a &quot;private forum&quot; that was only able to be seen by invitation of the boards administrators and unless you had been invited , there was no way for anyone to see what was there.<br>
The people on that board have said that the board was going to &quot;go public&quot; as soon as they had worked the kinks out of all the rules that they were hashing out. <br>
I was invited to this forum without any warning and when I realized it was a secret forum I posted a VERY ugly objection to it that can be read in the Book Club posting above.<br>
PLEASE don't take all I said to heart folks ... it was meant to be a wake up call to the members of that forum and only meant to get their attention by slapping them in the face.<br>
Since then other people have left over this incident and I am sorry that they felt a need to go . One of the warnings in my original rant was on that subject.<br>
<br>
This is to let you know that the people involved werent trying to block people out , nor were they trying to form a Guild within a Guild . They meant well but I believe the path they took to get there was incorrect and I told them that . This is what the blowup was over. <br>
<br>
Please remain calm and if you have any comments or need any clarification , post here or E Mail me at Bspinelli@CFL.RR.COM<br>
