online RPG for a few months. Saw a post from Sea<br>
about &quot;Earth and Beyond&quot;. I've read a little about it<br>
but haven't delved into it. I've been watching<br>
Asheron's Call 2 develop but haven't picked it up<br>
either. Anyone in Via tried it out yet?<br>
