months on end and had two or three going on a week<br>
for a while. But, it still happened and caused no end of<br>
stink while I worked to clear up the misunderstanding.<br>
Just life in the online world, I guess. Actually, the<br>
story is kind of a funny one of what _really_ happened,<br>
but I won't go into it now.  To all involved in the<br>
recent mess regarding &quot;Book Clubs&quot;, you have my<br>
sympathy.<br>
<br>
